    "As shown in Fig. 2a, the strategies to improve the energy density of the battery include the renovation from the material level (cathode, anode, electrolyte) as well as the device level (assembly, thickness and manufacturing).",
    "In terms of the material level, looking for an optimized cathode-anode pair with high theoretical capacity and voltage is on the top list of effective strategies.",
    "For the cathode, we are actively looking for new cathodes with high capacity and high voltage shown in Fig. 2b 28.",
    "For the anode applied for Li batteries, the theoretical capacity values of Li metal and Silicon anodes are 10 times higher than currently commercialized graphite.",
    "Thus, developing batteries with Li metal and Si anodes has become one of the most popular research directions in recent years."
